{"tid":429612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚係旺中附近俾個乞衣鬧","createTime":"2017-10-09T05:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T07:12:56.000Z","uid":58482,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6378164dcef63a7db9a7e0bc499be93a481b7655","tid":429612,"uid":58482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:21:52.000Z","msg":"尋晚十一點左右，我行緊去旺中附近巴士站等車<br />\n突然有個坐係卓悅門口嘅乞衣向住我大嗌<br />\n我開頭唔知佢鬧緊我，就冇理到繼續行<br />\n行到巴士站就停低等車，發現佢繼續向住我大嗌：有冇俾麻甩佬強姦啊？有冇啊？？？<br />\n當時好驚，不過好彩好快有車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打見過呢個人？唔敢再夜晚去旺角"},{"pid":"ebf4de1890fa47207226893f596a9309c994af60","tid":429612,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:24:44.000Z","msg":"咁即係有冇? 上次問你你都未答"},{"pid":"280be6bcf61dfb05f4671dc01719af1941fe5458","tid":429612,"uid":1582,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:30:03.000Z","msg":"人地問你野<br />\n答埋先走啦"},{"pid":"89e96116adb84a4ab1d1ff7785c9f6d1c89a1746","tid":429612,"uid":5044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:32:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地問你野<br />\n答埋先走啦</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"e02c051c2e610ee28d1731dc13ab059fc226783b","tid":429612,"uid":58482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:56:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁即係有冇? 上次問你你都未答</blockquote><br />\n你有冇俾麻甩佬雞姦過？有冇啊？？？"},{"pid":"eeb7f832a3f0ad3a7731cfe5d228f95bcce71705","tid":429612,"uid":3480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"死肥閪賤到乞衣都睇唔起你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\